Filter sensitivity across three lower cutoffs:
\begin{center}
\begin{tabular}{lc}
\toprule
$\mu_\text{min}$ & Tight-null hit fraction \\
\midrule
$0.7$~GeV (extrapolated) & $0.41\%$ \\
$1.0$~GeV (baseline) & $0.47\%$ \\
$1.5$~GeV & $0.58\%$ \\
$2.0$~GeV (excludes the observed lepton triple) & $0.00\%$ \\
